response.original_title: The Frank Sinatra Collection: Happy Holidays with Frank and Bing & Vintage Sinatra
response.overview: The Frank Sinatra Collection brings together some of Frank Sinatra's finest performances on television and in concert. This release combines a classic Christmas special from 1957 with a compilation from his 1950s TV shows.
